{"tid":311140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺公路交通意外 入上水車龍到馬窩","createTime":"2017-07-06T11:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T13:06:20.000Z","uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d141a2a02fa6f92a9d23b8d7f24d0fc859b3e99","tid":311140,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"【18:35】粉嶺公路往上水方向的車龍龍尾已到馬窩<br />\n<br />\n傍晚近6時，粉嶺公路和合石村對出發生交通意外，據報涉及旅遊巴及中型貨車，兩人受傷，救援人員到場將受傷人士送往醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，運輸署宣佈粉嶺公路往上水方向近和合石的慢線現已封閉，駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時在粉嶺公路往上水方向的車龍龍尾已到馬窩，上址交通擠塞。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170706&amp;guid=56922682&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170706%26guid%3D56922682%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=s1MGAAq8fjdDb2OMeQVui8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a1a49957\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170706%26guid%3D56922682%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=2624bdde\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170706&amp;guid=56922682&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n有無苦主同是天涯淪落人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d665461dc9f9b33eea4e8c8643cde53cc724875f","tid":311140,"uid":55023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ec278f9d9efc9fb24a46eac1b5ea033292b4db","tid":311140,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"放工時間炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />